{
  "stem": "1873.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot his first name, I think, David Lederman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is the price of your life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you forget, you're in trouble.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I will be in trouble.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went to this bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And later, I did get a crisis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember-- and I remember that this bed, it looked to me dirty, the-- the-- the-- the cover and everything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So always, I was asking they should give me to another bed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when they changed the beds, they changed the chart.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember some problems with the name, because when I have lost my mind, I said Lederman and sometimes not.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, I remember some troubles there was, but everything was fine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was actually a free man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If I would be healthy, I-- I could out to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But what's happened?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The policeman, the Jewish policeman, did show up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he told me, listen, you must be in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Until you pay me money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He wanted about 1,000 zlotys or whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You can't go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I told him, where should take the money?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't care.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Steal.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Without the money, you can't go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So, as long as I was still sick, everything was fine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But later, the doctor said, OK, you're OK.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You could go out from the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I told him, could I stay longer?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't want to tell him about the Jewish policeman, because it wasn't my doctor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was another doctor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I didn't want to tell him the truth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He didn't know about me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My doctor, I didn't see for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Otherwise, I would confide to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe he was-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and he said, no, you must go out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I signed you-- and he signed me out.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
